ocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T08:48:30.000Z","msg":"順便燒埋醫管局及選管會檔案"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:14:49.000Z","msg":"九龍灣國際展貿中心，早上8時57分，警方接報，指上址3至4樓位置發生火警，冒出大量濃煙，直捲半空。警方及消防到場，消防派出一隊煙帽隊開喉並架起雲梯灌救。消防搜救隊出動搜尋傷者，約半小時後消防將火救熄，期間近百人須疏散到地面，事件中無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1592965/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%B9%9D%E5%B1%95%E7%96%91%E9%9B%BB%E9%8C%B6%E6%88%BF%E8%B5%B7%E7%81%AB%E8%BF%91%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%BA%E7%96%8F%E6%95%A3-%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E5%82%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1592965%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25B1%2595%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%259B%25BB%25E9%258C%25B6%25E6%2588%25BF%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%2581%25AB%25E8%25BF%2591%25E7%2599%25BE%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2596%258F%25E6%2595%25A3-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2582%25B7&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2F0YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=4a4a345b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1592965%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25B1%2595%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%259B%25BB%25E9%258C%25B6%25E6%2588%25BF%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%2581%25AB%25E8%25BF%2591%25E7%2599%25BE%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2596%258F%25E6%2595%25A3-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2582%25B7&h=5657114b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1592965/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%B9%9D%E5%B1%95%E7%96%91%E9%9B%BB%E9%8C%B6%E6%88%BF%E8%B5%B7%E7%81%AB%E8%BF%91%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%BA%E7%96%8F%E6%95%A3-%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E5%82%B7</a>"},{"pid":"29c9330c183d8febbd699b12a2b4332eef7a7429","tid":1576410,"uid":345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:15:42.000Z","msg":"佢次次都大包圍又好難唔中嘅..."},{"pid":"d31df48d805f79c34535e6d31b752b81f7d83ceb","tid":1576410,"uid":169665,"like":0,"d